::Killfest/Greven/Goldeneye::

Killfest nods, walking off toward their destenation. He turns his 
head as Goldeneye runs out of the ship.

"Sorry, I got held up!" she says between breaths, running up to 
Killfest. Killfest nods and sets off again, Greven following him.
